From: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>
Date: Sun, 21 Jun 2026 20:13:16 +0000
Subject: [PATCH 2/2] branding: saved color-palette library + carry colors to
 new projects

Add an account-level library of color schemes you build over time and pick
from per project. Fix colors not following to new projects: global save now
persists primary/accent + the palette library, and pre-fill seeds empty color
slots from the account default. Past projects are never rewritten.

Code degrades gracefully if the new color_palettes column is unmigrated.

Co-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.8 (1M context) <noreply@anthropic.com>
